commit.message:
mips.exp (setup_mips_tests): Fix _MIPS_SIM conditions.

gcc/testsuite/
	* gcc.target/mips/mips.exp (setup_mips_tests): Fix _MIPS_SIM
	conditions.
	(dg-mips-options): Treat -march=24k* as a 32-bit option.
